      },
      "notes": [
        {
          "category": "summary",
          "text": "The affected device stores sensitive information in cleartext, which may allow an authenticated user to access session data stored in the OAuth database belonging to legitimate users.CVE-2022-2569 has been assigned to this vulnerability. A CVSS v3 base score of 5.5 has been assigned; the CVSS vector string is (AV:L/AC:L/PR:L/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:N/A:N).\n\u00a0",
          "title": "Vulnerability Summary"
